{"tid":1979893,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【女團個人品牌評價】華莎重返冠軍寶座　(G)I-DLE 三人打入前十名！","createTime":"2020-04-19T17:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T17:57:32.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dfc5524870b03b35ac7fc470f6203b0904156099","tid":1979893,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T17:56:28.000Z","msg":"在最新出爐的女團成員品牌評價前十名中，有正在打歌的偶像，也有人氣始終火熱者。其中前三名的共通點，就是獨樹一幟的時尚感！<br />\n<br />\n韓國企業評價研究所於 2020 年 3 月 18 日起至 2020 年 4 月 19 日間，針對韓國人民喜愛的 510 位女團成員搜集了 66,586,018 件數據，並就品牌參與、互動、媒體表現、社群價值⋯⋯等項目進行分析，並在今天（19 日）公布了 4 月份的女團個人品牌評價結果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時隔三個月，MAMAMOO 老么華莎再度回到冠軍寶座。活躍在綜藝節目、廣告圈的她也不忘歌手身份，最近除了和 Dua Lipa 合唱了 &ldquo;Physical&rdquo; 外，也為電視劇《The King》唱了 OST &ldquo;Orbit&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n而經常一起出現在前三名內的 BLACKPINK 成員 Jennie 和 Red Velvet 成員 Joy，本月也依序拿下二、三名。深受各種品牌青睞的兩人，即使在非打歌期間，仍透過 Instagram 分享穿搭而備受關注。<br />\n<br />\n除了上述三人外，Apink 的孫娜恩、Red Velvet 隊長 Irene、少女時代隊長太妍、(G)I-DLE 隊長小娟、IZ*ONE 張員瑛、(G)I-DLE 的穗珍和薇娟（美延）也都依序打入了前十名中。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_bf9f542fe9b527274cafdeba7fc11501/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-04-19/126048-832968.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_bf9f542fe9b527274cafdeba7fc11501%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-04-19%2F126048-832968.jpg&h=8c8e7bba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（照片或影片來源：RBW、jennierubyjane、_imyour_joy、Stone Music Entertainment）"},{"pid":"0945d707d92790967a4844869b25c59cd2880371","tid":1979893,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T17:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_36334b44eac2e9dcef0d1ddafabd2e3f/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-04-19/126048-832963.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_36334b44eac2e9dcef0d1ddafabd2e3f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-04-19%2F126048-832963.png&h=a75fad64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d114e38884f1f5bc9cb61dcfcddea6285417032","tid":1979893,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T17:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_37e9000b41aa894787d0818feb891c9d/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-04-19/126048-832964.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_37e9000b41aa894787d0818feb891c9d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-04-19%2F126048-832964.jpg&h=ff682c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_171f36aeb1a5f8754c0e8adaa700e9de/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-04-19/126048-832966.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_171f36aeb1a5f8754c0e8adaa700e9de%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-04-19%2F126048-832966.jpg&h=32e46c04&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}